Also suggest music piece that could accompany artwork nicely depending upon its genre/style type along with appropriate reference images demonstrating your recommendations regarding same;
all this in order to help out aspiring artists explore new creative possibilities and practice ideas which will further help them sharpen their skills accordingly!
First request - "I'm making surrealistic portrait paintings"

